801
00:42:58,259 --> 00:42:59,351
All right. OK.

802
00:42:59,427 --> 00:43:00,894
Why don't you just
get on your way, OK?

803
00:43:00,962 --> 00:43:02,429
Act like you never met us.

804
00:43:02,496 --> 00:43:04,157
Send us a postcard
from Crazy Town.

805
00:43:04,232 --> 00:43:05,324
Can I stay here?

806
00:43:05,399 --> 00:43:07,560
Just that I don't know
where else to go.

807
00:43:08,469 --> 00:43:10,027
It'll only be one night.

808
00:43:10,104 --> 00:43:11,196
Please?

809
00:43:11,272 --> 00:43:12,637
I'm not sure we can do that.

810
00:43:12,707 --> 00:43:14,504
Absolutely no way. There's...

811
00:43:14,575 --> 00:43:15,667
That's not possible.

812
00:43:15,743 --> 00:43:17,472
I can't go home.

813
00:43:17,578 --> 00:43:19,273
I can't.

814
00:43:19,380 --> 00:43:21,348
I could go to the police.

815
00:43:21,449 --> 00:43:23,076
I mean, what's to stop me
leading them...

816
