00:43:28,022 --> 00:43:29,114
I mean, he wouldn't tell me.

819
00:43:29,190 --> 00:43:30,714
He's very, very discreet.

820
00:43:30,791 --> 00:43:32,224
Come here, Joe. Come here.

821
00:43:32,293 --> 00:43:33,783
What are you...
What's with the pulling?

