825
00:43:41,269 --> 00:43:42,998
No. She's right
about the police.

826
00:43:43,070 --> 00:43:44,162
Shoot her.

827
00:43:44,238 --> 00:43:45,603
Bury her body in the woods.

828
00:43:45,673 --> 00:43:47,504
