829
00:43:47,575 --> 00:43:49,270
She said she doesn't have
anyplace to stay.

830
00:43:49,343 --> 00:43:50,503
It's none of our business.

831
00:43:50,611 --> 00:43:51,737
It is now that you
brought her here, isn't it?

832
00:43:51,846 --> 00:43:53,837
Well, I needed a ride, OK?

833
00:43:53,948 --> 00:43:57,247
I mean, there I was,
sprawled out on the asphalt, OK?

834
00:43:58,252 --> 00:44:00,152
You know the hardest thing
about being smart?

835
00:44:00,988 --> 00:44:02,080
No.

836
00:44:02,156 --> 00:44:04,021
I always pretty much know
what's gonna happen next.

837
00:44:04,091 --> 00:44:05,786
There's no suspense.

838
00:44:05,860 --> 00:44:06,952
And don't think I didn't see...

839
