I'm implementing a 24-hour rule
from now on, OK?

842
00:44:13,768 --> 00:44:15,099
It's in effect.

843
00:44:15,703 --> 00:44:16,795
Twenty-four hours.

844
00:44:16,871 --> 00:44:18,839
Twenty-four hours and not
a minute longer, missy.

845
00:44:18,906 --> 00:44:19,838
Thank you.

846
00:44:19,907 --> 00:44:21,169
"Missy."

847
00:44:21,742 --> 00:44:23,403
Hey. I'll cook dinner.

848
00:44:23,477 --> 00:44:25,240
I cook the dinners around here.

849
00:44:25,346 --> 00:44:27,906
Sorry. Not familiar
with the outlaw code.

850
00:44:28,849 --> 00:44:30,976
Does that mean I'm a hostage?

851
00:44:32,153 --> 00:44:33,415
Well, I was in Las Vegas.

852
00:44:33,487 --> 00:44:34,579
Don't get excited.

853
00:44:34,655 --> 00:44:35,986
