856
00:44:40,528 --> 00:44:43,190
I've estimated $20,000
for the kitchen alone.

857
00:44:43,264 --> 00:44:45,858
I mean, we're talking
about restaurant quality here...

858
00:44:45,933 --> 00:44:47,298
