00:46:10,518 --> 00:46:12,418
Oh, of course you did.

903
00:46:12,486 --> 00:46:14,215
- The Netherlands.
- Yeah.

904
00:46:14,288 --> 00:46:16,415
Joe.

905
00:46:16,490 --> 00:46:17,616
What?

906
00:46:18,626 --> 00:46:19,752
Listen.

907
00:46:22,229 --> 00:46:23,787
Let me try to explain
something to you.

908
00:46:23,864 --> 00:46:26,389
Paradise doesn't
come cheaply, OK?

