00:46:27,034 --> 00:46:29,662
Now, I've figured this
down to the last nickel.

910
00:46:29,737 --> 00:46:31,762
Now, and here's
the important part...

911
00:46:31,839 --> 00:46:33,602
every nickel that we spend...

912
00:46:33,674 --> 00:46:35,335
