that we have to steal.

913
00:46:35,409 --> 00:46:36,740
Now, that's a lot
of nickels, Joe.

914
00:46:36,811 --> 00:46:39,803
I don't want to rob banks
for the rest of my life.

915
00:46:39,914 --> 00:46:42,678
The stress level
is just too damned high.

916
00:46:43,951 --> 00:46:45,384
Harvey?

917
00:46:45,453 --> 00:46:46,545
Joe?

918
00:46:46,620 --> 00:46:48,053
Dinner's almost ready.

919
00:46:49,490 --> 00:46:51,117
Now, this is not bad.

920
00:46:52,159 --> 00:46:53,285
It's a little...

921
00:46:54,028 --> 00:46:55,962
It's a little chewy, but...

