928
00:47:26,193 --> 00:47:27,319
Harvey.

929
00:47:28,128 --> 00:47:29,595
That's enough, Harvey.

930
00:47:31,565 --> 00:47:32,657
Wait a minute.

931
00:47:32,733 --> 00:47:33,927
You're not the...

932
00:47:34,001 --> 00:47:35,730
the guys who go to
the bank manager's house...

933
00:47:35,803 --> 00:47:37,134
you know,
the night before, and you...

934
00:47:37,204 --> 00:47:38,762
