I drive the getaway car.

935
00:47:38,839 --> 00:47:40,500
Harvey!

936
00:47:41,475 --> 00:47:43,102
For the love of God.

937
00:47:47,214 --> 00:47:49,682
You're the Sleepover Bandits.

938
00:47:51,151 --> 00:47:53,585
Oh, my God,
you're practically famous.

939
00:47:53,687 --> 00:47:56,622
The Sleepover Bandits?

940
00:47:56,690 --> 00:47:57,816
That's us?

941
00:47:58,826 --> 00:48:01,124
Don't you watch
"Criminals at Large"?

942
00:48:01,195 --> 00:48:02,526
You should.

943
00:48:02,596 --> 00:48:04,359
They're watching you.

944
00:48:04,431 --> 00:48:06,228
You're astounding, Harvey.

945
00:48:06,300 --> 00:48:08,291
So...

946
00:48:08,369 --> 00:48:09,700
you rob banks.

947
00:48:09,770 --> 00:48:10,998
Well, that's impressive.

948
00:48:11,071 --> 00:48:12,868
What, some little old ladies'
savings accounts...

949
00:48:12,940 --> 00:48:16,103
and Cub Scout dues and homeless
orphan Christmas funds?

