00:48:16,176 --> 00:48:17,609
Is that what...

951
00:48:19,847 --> 00:48:22,782
We never stole a penny from
anybody who earned it, lady.

952
00:48:24,451 --> 00:48:27,215
That money's federally insured
by the government.

953
00:48:28,856 --> 00:48:30,187
The government
steals money from people...

954
00:48:30,257 --> 00:48:32,020
and we just take it
back from them.

955
00:48:40,034 --> 00:48:42,468
Any more questions, Kate?

956
00:48:51,178 --> 00:48:53,305
Got a spare toothbrush?

957
00:48:53,414 --> 00:48:55,279
Didn't have time to pack.

958
00:48:56,584 --> 00:48:58,108
God, nobody could be that sick.

959
00:48:58,218 --> 00:49:00,083
Put that down.

960
00:49:03,057 --> 00:49:04,319
May I?

961
00:49:05,326 --> 00:49:07,089
What are you doing here?

962
00:49:07,161 --> 00:49:08,253
