are on your finger?

967
00:49:16,670 --> 00:49:18,831
That kind of
defeats the purpose.

968
00:49:18,906 --> 00:49:20,237
Well, if you don't
give me a toothbrush...

969
00:49:20,307 --> 00:49:22,434
I don't have much option, do I?

970
00:49:25,379 --> 00:49:27,939
I don't think you're crazy
at all, you know that?

971
00:49:28,048 --> 00:49:29,481
I think you're bored.

972
00:49:29,550 --> 00:49:31,484
I think you're bored
with your life...

973
