983
00:50:01,215 --> 00:50:03,115
How does it end?

984
00:50:04,385 --> 00:50:05,818
With a wedding.

985
00:50:15,829 --> 00:50:17,456
Beavers and ducks!

986
00:50:18,899 --> 00:50:20,594
Suckers.

987
00:50:20,668 --> 00:50:23,660
I'm not waiting for anything
to fall out of the sky.

988
00:50:23,737 --> 00:50:25,864
I'm not bored. I'm angry.

989
00:50:31,245 --> 00:50:33,577
Maybe he's right
about running out of hope.

990
00:50:33,681 --> 00:50:35,273
It's not entirely my fault.

991
00:50:36,250 --> 00:50:38,741
It's just that I picked
the wrong life.

992
00:50:51,365 --> 00:50:53,333
The valley spirit is a woman.

993
00:50:54,601 --> 00:50:56,899
Use her root
at the gateway of heaven...

994
00:50:56,970 --> 00:50:59,029
