995
00:50:59,106 --> 00:51:02,507
What the hell
is that supposed to mean?

996
00:51:03,610 --> 00:51:04,736
Not a clue.

997
00:51:06,613 --> 00:51:07,705
I'm hoping that it means...

998
00:51:07,815 --> 00:51:10,079
figure out what you want
and just take it.

999
00:51:10,851 --> 00:51:12,443
Oh, please.

1000
00:51:13,253 --> 00:51:16,188
What, like robbing a bank?

1001
00:51:16,256 --> 00:51:17,723
Like that. Yeah.

1002
00:51:18,926 --> 00:51:21,224
If only life were that simple.

1003
00:51:25,232 --> 00:51:28,201
Like a shadow on me
all of the time

1004
00:51:30,838 --> 00:51:32,430
I don't know what to do.

1005
00:51:33,340 --> 00:51:35,240
I'm always in the dark.

1006
00:51:36,243 --> 00:51:38,871
We're living in a powder keg,
giving off sparks.

1007
