Once upon a time,
I was falling in love.

1008
00:51:50,791 --> 00:51:53,385
Now I'm only falling apart.

1009
00:51:54,795 --> 00:51:56,558
Nothing I can do.

1010
00:51:56,630 --> 00:51:58,257
Total eclipse of the heart.

1011
00:52:05,205 --> 00:52:08,106
Once upon a time,
there was light in my life.

1012
00:52:08,175 --> 00:52:10,473
Now there's only
love in the dark.

1013
00:52:11,578 --> 00:52:13,341
Nothing I can do.

1014
00:52:13,447 --> 00:52:15,039
Total eclipse of the heart.

1015
00:52:16,950 --> 00:52:19,111
Oh, my God.

1016
00:52:19,186 --> 00:52:20,483
Give me a break.

1017
00:52:21,588 --> 00:52:24,079
Turn around, bright eyes.

1018
00:52:24,758 --> 00:52:26,885
I can't believe
you know that song.

1019
00:52:28,629 --> 00:52:29,891
Yeah. Bonnie Tyler.

1020
00:52:29,963 --> 00:52:31,555
"Total Eclipse of the Heart."

1021
00:52:31,632 --> 00:52:33,566
It's the ultimate
sappy chick song.

1022
00:52:33,634 --> 00:52:35,727
- It's not a sappy chick song.
