1023
00:52:35,803 --> 00:52:36,895
No, it's not.

1024
00:52:36,970 --> 00:52:38,494
Oh, please don't argue.
I'm having a really hard day.

1025
00:52:38,572 --> 00:52:40,199
This is the song
that all girls sing...

1026
00:52:40,274 --> 00:52:41,605
It is an epic haiku to the...

