00:52:47,881 --> 00:52:51,146
When that song was out, I used
to listen to it on the radio.

1031
00:52:52,186 --> 00:52:56,088
I have to admit,
I would get a little misty.

1032
00:52:56,190 --> 00:52:57,487
Really?

1033
00:52:57,558 --> 00:52:59,321
Yeah, a little...

1034
00:52:59,793 --> 00:53:03,752
