00:53:34,661 --> 00:53:35,753
You know that song?

1043
00:53:35,829 --> 00:53:38,889
Oh, I love that pony song.

1044
00:53:38,966 --> 00:53:40,490
- You do?
- I love all pony songs.

1045
00:53:40,567 --> 00:53:42,000
- Really? You know...
- Yeah.

1046
00:53:42,069 --> 00:53:43,161
It's the one that goes...

